nodes.text: Tyreese was a human male who lived on the planet of Tatooine during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. A Weaponmaster, Tyreese had a shop in the Anchorhead market where he built and sold weapons.

Tyreese was created for Star Wars: The Old Republic, a massively multiplayer online role-playing game released by BioWare on December 20, 2011. He appears in Anchorhead, the Republic-only city on Tatooine, as an Armstech Crew Skill trainer.
